hopobject.body: Will I have to work shifts? l-arginine 4g Ryan pointed out that the Jets got to two AFC Championship Games in his first two seasons, and he said he didn’t always watch the offense during those seasons, either. And Ryan says that other coaches are no different than he is: Sometimes they turn around to talk to a player or assistant coach or deal with some issue on the other side of the ball, and miss some of the live game action.
